Data Structures
Here are the data structures with brief descriptions:
 CNOR_DataUnion for Nor data
 CNOR_INFO_Struct to hold discovered flash parameters
 CNor_InitPrms_tStruct to hold Init parametrs for Nor flash
 CNOR_PtrUnion for Nor data pointer
 CQSPI_ConfigDesc_tStruct to hold configuration descriptor type
 CQSPI_FlashCmd_tStruct to hold QSPI flash command parameters
 CQSPI_FlashDevInfo_tStruct to hold QSPI flash device info
 CsbllibAppImageParseParamsThis structure defines the multi-core application image parse parameters
 CsbllibEntryPointsThis structure defines the Entry Points for different cores
 CsbllibInitParamsThis structure defines the SBL lib Initialization parameters
 CsbllibMetaHeaderCoreV1This structure defines the core meta header of multi-core app image for version 1 of Multi-core header
 CsbllibMetaHeaderCoreV2This structure defines the core meta header of multi-core app image for version 2 of Multi-core header
 CsbllibMetaHeaderEndThis structure defines the end of meta header of multi-core app image
 CsbllibMetaHeaderStartV1This structure defines the start of meta header of multi-core app image for version 1 of Multi-core header
 CsbllibMetaHeaderStartV2This structure defines the start of meta header of multi-core app image for version 2 of Multi-core header
 CsbllibMetaHeaderV1This structure contains the all individual headers required for the version 1 of meta header of multi-core app image
 CsbllibMetaHeaderV2This structure contains the all individual headers required for the version 2 of meta header of multi-core app image
 CsbllibRprcFileHeaderThis structure defines the file header of RPRC image
 CsbllibRPRCImageHeaderThis structure contains the all individual headers required for the RPRC header of multi-core app image
 CsbllibRprcSectionHeaderThis structure defines the section header of RPRC image
 CsblutilsClockDomainStateConfigThis structure defines the Clock Domain's configuration for configuring state of clock domain
 CsblutilsDelayConfigThis structure defines the delay configuration for IO Delay Config Registers: CFG_X_IN, CFG_X_OUT and CFG_X_OEN
 CsblutilsDelayConfigRegValueThis structure is used to store the calculated delay values to be configured in CFG_X_IN, CFG_X_OUT and CFG_X_OEN Registers
 CsblutilsModuleEnableConfigThis structure defines the Module's configuration for enabling Module mode
 CsblutilsPadDelayConfigThis structure defines the delay configuration associated with a particular pad as given by PCT (Pad Configuration Tool)
 CsblutilsPowerDomainStateConfigThis structure defines the Power Domain's configuration for configuring state of Power domain
